title: FIFA Coupe du Monde 98 finale Bresil-France
description:
Coupe du Monde de la FIFA France 98
Finale du 12 juillet 1998 : Bresil - France
Match integral avec commentaires francais (image TF1), remise de la coupe et apres-match.
Qualite moyenne, rip provenant d'une cassette VHS.
_________________________

1998 FIFA 16th World Cup, held in France.
Final contested between Brazil and France on July 12th.
Entire match with french commentators (channel TF1), World Cup presentation and afterwards.
Not huge quality, was ripped from an VHS tape. Sorry Brazilian anthem is missing.
